text: Asovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Asovskoye Rural Settlement, Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 826 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km south-east from Beryozovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai
title: Asovo
